 very young, we joined the Band of Hope, and - Alice used to sing, and at one - week they gave out, Miss Carlile will sing - a lullaby song, now my dad had bought - two - two dolls, very beautiful dolls they were. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Alice{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} had one I had the other. So the part when they said, Miss Carlile will now stand up and sing, we were neither of us on the platform, so \{BLANK\}
 Because I thought it was my sister going to sing it you know. It wasn't, it was me, and they wouldn't all listen to me.
